@startuml TrailSocial_Token_Refresh
!theme plain
title Обновление токена (Token Refresh) - Sequence Diagram

participant "Any Screen" as Screen
participant "ViewModel" as VM
participant "Repository" as Repo
participant "OkHttpClient" as OkHttp
participant "AuthInterceptor" as AI
participant "TokenManager" as TM
participant "TokenAuthenticator" as TA
participant "AuthApi" as AuthAPI
database "Backend API" as BE

== Обычный запрос с валидным токеном ==

Screen -> VM : action()
VM -> Repo : fetchData()
Repo -> OkHttp : GET /routes
OkHttp -> AI : intercept(chain)
AI -> TM : getAccessToken()
TM --> AI : "eyJhbG..."
AI -> AI : request.newBuilder()\n.header("Authorization",\n"Bearer eyJhbG...")
AI -> BE : HTTP request + Bearer token
BE --> OkHttp : 200 OK + data
OkHttp --> Repo : Response
Repo --> VM : ApiResult.Success(data)

== Токен истёк → автоматическое обновление ==

Screen -> VM : action()
VM -> Repo : fetchData()
Repo -> OkHttp : GET /routes
OkHttp -> AI : intercept(chain)
AI -> TM : getAccessToken()
TM --> AI : "expired_token"
AI -> BE : HTTP request + expired token
BE --> OkHttp : **401 Unauthorized**

OkHttp -> TA : authenticate(route, response)
note right of TA : responseCount < 2\n→ можно retry

TA -> TM : getRefreshToken()
TM --> TA : "refresh_token_value"

TA -> AuthAPI : POST /auth/refresh\n{refresh_token}
AuthAPI -> BE : HTTP POST
BE --> AuthAPI : 200 {new_access, new_refresh}
AuthAPI --> TA : TokenResponse

TA -> TM : saveTokens(\nnew_access, new_refresh)

TA -> TA : response.request\n.newBuilder()\n.header("Authorization",\n"Bearer new_access")
TA --> OkHttp : Retried request

OkHttp -> BE : Original request\n+ new token
BE --> OkHttp : 200 OK + data
OkHttp --> Repo : Response
Repo --> VM : ApiResult.Success(data)

== Refresh token тоже истёк → выход ==

Screen -> VM : action()
VM -> Repo : fetchData()
Repo -> OkHttp : GET /routes
BE --> OkHttp : **401 Unauthorized**

OkHttp -> TA : authenticate(route, response)
TA -> TM : getRefreshToken()
TM --> TA : "expired_refresh"

TA -> AuthAPI : POST /auth/refresh
AuthAPI -> BE : HTTP POST
BE --> AuthAPI : **401 Unauthorized**

TA -> TM : clearTokens()
note right of TM : isLoggedIn\nemits false

TA --> OkHttp : return null\n(no retry)
OkHttp --> Repo : 401 Response
Repo --> VM : ApiResult.Error(401)

note over Screen : AppNavigation\nobserves isLoggedIn = false\n→ LoginScreen

@enduml
